column1: Results from the 2002 IBSA World Powerlifting Championships
September 19th - 22nd at the Centrum of Disabled Sports in Ceske Budejovice, Czech Republic.
Women's Combined Gold: Edie Jones, USA, Wilks = 290.7
Women's Combined Silver: Radka Houљkovб, Czech, Wilks = 231.6
Women's Combined Bronze: Petra Duљkovб, Czech, Wilks = 225.1
Men's Combined Gold: Serguei Chatalov, Russia, Wilks = 424.6
Men's Combined Silver: Cody Colchado, USA, Wilks = 403.1
Men's Combined Bronze: Jiri Janouљek, Czech, Wilks = 401.9
John Baxter Most Improved Lifter Award
Tim Ekert, from 552.5k to 610.0k for a 57.5k improvement
